        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 17 at 6:13PM MDT until July 17 at 6:45PM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 612 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 10 miles northeast
of Zortman, moving southeast at 35 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage to
roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Zortman, Phillips, and Landusky.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

This storm will travel over Highway 191 near Phillips and Zortman.</instruction>
